        </h3>
        <select
          value="{{ timeRange }}"
          class="pl-3 pr-8 py-1.5 text-gray-900 text-sm dark:text-neutral-100 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-neutral-600 border-0 ring-1 ring-gray-300 ring-inset rounded-md dark:ring-neutral-600 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-600"
        >
          <option value="7">Last 7 days</option>
